）。\r\n中　　華　　民　　國　　110 　年　　12　　月　　23　　日\r\n                                  書記官　張鈞雅","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TNEV/110%2c%e5%8d%97%e7%b0%a1%2c1609%2c20211223%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TNEV,110,南簡,1609,20211223,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"南簡","JNO":"1609","JDATE":"20211223","JTITLE":"清償借款"}